<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Response to Your Question</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #1900fe;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Hello, <%= name %></h2>
        <p>We have received your question regarding the course <strong>"<%= title %>"</strong>.</p>
        <p>We have added our response</p>
        <p>If you have any further questions, feel free to ask.</p>
        <p>Best Regards,</p>
        <p><strong>GenZTechno</strong></p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated email. Please do not reply directly.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
